Before using the face ID function, please keep the following precautions in mind： 
1.Your car account may be listed by people or items similar to you in appearance and appearance. 
2.The security of face recognition is lower than that of pattern cipher, digital cipher and hybrid cipher. 
3.In the case of dark light, strong light, backlight or too large angle, the success rate of face recognition will be reduced. 
4.Do not hand over the vehicle to others for use at will to avoid the malicious use of face ID function. 
5.In addition to the above scenarios, there may be other situations that affect the normal use of face ID function in reality, which you need to pay attention to. 
In order to better use face ID function, please pay attention to the following items when entering face data: 
1.Please make sure that there is sufficient light, avoid direct sunlight and avoid other people appearing in the input screen. 
2.Please pay attention to the face status when entering data, and avoid the clothes, hair, sunglasses, masks, heavy makeup, etc. blocking the face information. 
3.Please avoid looking up, looking down, closing eyes or only showing the side face, and make sure that the front face is clear and complete in the prompt box. 
If you agree to this statement and input the face data (the face data will be encrypted and saved locally in your vehicle), the system will turn on the face ID function.
